      "content": "i know there are people to talk to but what's the point? everyone just looks at you differently once you're a failure. i keep thinking about how much easier it would be if i just didn't have to wake up tomorrow and face this. if i'm already at the bottom, i might as well just stay here. it feels like the only way to stop the sinking.",
